rights while riding the bus. J. ALBERT DIAZ / Los Angeles Times; Photo, RTD 
Officer Rod Evans checks out bus on Broadway. The agency added foot patrols to 
an eight-block stretch of the downtown business district. ; Photo, (A1) COLOR, 
RTD officers on bus. J. ALBERT DIAZ / Los Angeles Times 
</P>
