among the crowd at a Vons market in Montebello protesting pesticide use on 
grapes. United Farm Workers leader Cesar Chavez, two of his school-age 
granddaughters and nine other supporters were arrested after defying a court 
order to stop picketing the markets. ; Photo, United Farm Workers leader Cesar 
