<TEXT>
<P>
William I. Campbell, a senior vice president at Philip Morris Cos., New York, 
has been appointed head of the firm's domestic tobacco business, Philip Morris 
U.S.A. Campbell replaces Ehud Houminer, who was appointed a senior vice 
president of Philip Morris Management Corp. Houminer will be involved in 
"special projects of a strategic nature." 
</P>
